name: Kharisma Bahari
description: This graphic art was created, when David Wirawan P first lived in the capital city of Indonesia, there was a food stall that he always went to when he was hungry. The price never differs from the first day to the end of the month, only 15 thousand Rupiah will make your stomach full without waiting for a discount. God bless you Warung Tegal Kharisma Bahari!
